-- Dubai International Says Court Confirms New Almatis Reorganization Plan
-- Ben Livesey
-- 2010-09-20T20:19:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-20/dubai-international-says-court-confirms-new-almatis-reorganization-plan.html

          
          
             Dubai International Capital LLC
said the bankruptcy court for the Southern District of New York
today confirmed Almatis Group’s amended plan of reorganization.  
 DIC is “confident of a strong future” for Almatis and
expects the company to exit Chapter 11 “very shortly,” it said
in an e-mailed statement.  
          
          


  


        